text=*[[eyeo, t-shirt->http://www.stefanieposavec.co.uk/data/#/eyeo-2013-t-shirt/]]: This t-shirt sums up how I often enjoy working with data: a passerby on the street would only see a nice t-shirt. However, for the wearer of the tshirt, the design has more meaning, as they know how to interpret the design, and, once they offer this information to someone new, the t-shirt design takes on another layer of meaning. %0a%0a*[[chromosonic->http://ejtech.cc/]]: Trying out alternative approaches for interfaces to control software through MIDI. Screen printed Musical Instrument Digital Interface controller on canvas.%0a%0a*[[n-e-r-v-o-u-s->https://n-e-r-v-o-u-s.com/cellCycle/]]:  We create our designs through an iterative and experimental process. After brainstorming an initial concept, we write a pattern generating algorithm through which we further explore our ideas and ultimately create a finished product. You can use the software we share here to create your own one of a kind designs or just to play and learn. %0a%0a*[['''Esquemáticos'''->http://www.amormunoz.net/index.php?/en-proceso/e-s-q-u-e-m-a-t-i-c-o-s/]]: Esquemáticos is a series of works that link hand-made embroidering with the symbolic representation of analogue circuit diagrams. The project is an exhibition of large schematic drawings that have been hand-sewn with a conductive thread and electronic components, so that the circuits are fully functional machines that can be operated by the public.%0a%0a*[['''Quilting + Generative Design = Wrap Yourself in Code '''->http://libselliott.blogspot.com.es/]]:Projecte de hacking textil amb processing, per crear motius inspirats en el glitchr amb motius per Libs Elliott.%0a%0a*[['''Meet The Tacit Project. It’s Sonar For The Blind'''->http://grathio.com/2011/08/meet-the-tacit-project-its-sonar-for-the-blind/]]: This is a project I’m calling Tacit. No, I didn’t bother making an awkward backronym for it, it just seemed like an appropriate name that’s a lot shorter (though less descriptive) than “Hand-Mounted Haptic Feedback Sonar Obstacle Avoidance Asstance Device”.  It measures the distance to things and translates that into pressure on the wrist.%0a%0a*[['''Electricfoxy talks with Asta Roseway at MR''', 2011->http://vimeo.com/26806334]]: Treball d'un laboratori per innovar amb els teixits i la utilització dels elements electrònics integrats en la moda.%0a%0a*[['''When Haute Couture meets High Tech!''',2011->http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TFfWuR0EQmw&feature=youtu.be]]: Conductive embroidery lights up the Climate Dress by DIFFUS %0a%0a*[['''Hussein Chalayan spring summer''',2007->http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wXaONmuCgWE&feature=youtu.be]]: El disseny i el canvi i modificació del mateix al moment és una de les possibilitats que s'estableix en aquest video.%0a%0a*[['''The New BUI'''->http://www.fashioningtech.com/profiles/blogs/assembly-the-new-bui]]: Amb la tecnologia portàtil sorgeixen noves necessitats d'interacció amb els usuaris.%0a%0a*[['''Smartcraftlab'''->http://smartcraftlab.wordpress.com/]]: bloc dedicat a la interacció amb Lilypad Arduino%0a%0a* [['''RolandPad'''->http://vimeo.com/38598247]]: teclat bordat interactuant amb lilypad
